body:
markdo.gitbub.io
================

Pages for documenting metricsgreimoire and Vizgreimoire*
Just trying to learn how to use these in case we want to create *documentation* for it.
* document how to use the tools end to end, starting with metricsgrimoire.
* give detailed instructions for use of the viz* code.
* provide concrete examaples.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
